    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-03-01T18:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-03-01T18:00:00-05:00" n="438"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d438">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. No. 763.72112/7397a</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in Honduras</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_CCB1" type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Curtis</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-03-01T18:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 1, 1918, 6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Department’s January 21, 7 p.m.,<note n="1" xml:id="d438fn1">
                        <hi rend="italic">Ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_380">p. 380</ref>.</note>
                    first paragraph, and Department’s January 5, 8 p.m.<note n="2" xml:id="d438fn2">
                        <hi rend="italic">Ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_376">p. 376</ref>.</note>
                </p>
                <p>The United States Government is now prepared to make exhaustive survey of channel
                    to and island of Sacate Grande. Obtain formal permission of Honduran Government
                    for making such survey, also permission to land and store at Amapala gasoline
                    necessary for carrying out operations.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_LR1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
